op_master_id: (SELECT KI.KI AS KI, K.KICD AS KICD, RTRIM(K.KCOD) AS KCOD, K.KNMX AS KNMX, K.KNAM AS KNAM, K.KNLD AS KNLD, K.KOCD AS KOCD, K.KATT AS KATT, K.GSW1 AS GSW1, K.GSW2 AS GSW2, K.SY01 AS SY01, K.SY02 AS SY02, K.SY03 AS SY03, K.SY04 AS SY04, K.SY05 AS SY05, K.SY06 AS SY06, K.SY07 AS SY07, K.SY08 AS SY08, K.KE02 AS KE02, K.KT02 AS KT02, K.KB02 AS KB02, K.BKE01 AS BKE01, K.SG02 AS SG02, K.PJ02 AS PJ02, :DM1 AS UF12, :DM2 AS UF22, :DM3 AS UF32, K.KJ02 AS KJ02, K.KS02 AS KS02, K.TK02 AS TK02, K.BTK01 AS BTK01, K.BTKE01 AS BTKE01, K.TKE01 AS TKE01, K.STK01 AS STK01, K.KK01 AS KK01 FROM AEXP.A_KI AS KI JOIN dbo.KNAME AS K ON K.KESN = KI.KESN)

(select KI.KI AS KI, Z.KICD AS KICD, RTRIM(Z.ECOD) AS ECOD, RTRIM(K.KCOD) AS KCOD, K.KOCD AS KOCD, K.KNMX AS KNMX, K.KNAM AS KNAM, K.KATT AS KATT, CAST( CASE WHEN E.ENSG = 1 THEN E.ENAM WHEN E.TCOD IS NULL THEN '' ELSE ISNULL((SELECT Z.TNAM FROM dbo.ZMTKY Z WHERE Z.KESN = E.KESN AND Z.TCOD = E.TCOD), '') END AS CHAR(20) ) AS ENAM, 0 as K000 from AEXP.A_KI as KI join dbo.EDZAN as Z on Z.KESN = KI.KESN join dbo.KNAME as K on K.KESN = Z.KESN and K.KICD = Z.KICD join dbo.ENAME as E on E.KESN = Z.KESN and E.KICD = Z.KICD and E.ECOD = Z.ECOD)
(SELECT KI.KI AS KI, RTRIM(B.BCOD) AS BCOD, B.BNAM AS BNAM, B.BNLD BNLD, B.BFLG AS BFLG FROM AEXP.A_KI AS KI JOIN dbo.BNAME AS B ON B.KESN = KI.KESN AND B.BFLG = '0')

(select KI.KI AS KI, RTRIM(Z.BCOD) AS BCOD, Z.KICD AS KICD, B.BNAM AS BNAM, RTRIM(K.KCOD) AS KCOD, K.KOCD AS KOCD, K.KNMX AS KNMX, K.KNAM AS KNAM, K.KATT AS KATT, 0 as K000 from AEXP.A_KI as KI join dbo.BKZAN as Z on Z.KESN = KI.KESN join dbo.BNAME as B on B.KESN = Z.KESN and B.BCOD = Z.BCOD join dbo.KNAME as K on K.KESN = Z.KESN and K.KICD = Z.KICD)
(SELECT RTRIM(T.TRCD) AS TRCD, T.TRMX AS TRMX, T.TRNAM AS TRNAM, T.RNLD AS RNLD FROM dbo.TRNAM T)

(SELECT TR.TRCD, TR.ZIP, TR.ADDR1, TR.ADDR2, TR.TEL, TR.FAX, FR.MEIGI, FR.MEIGIK, SK.SKBKIND, FR.YOKIN_TYP, FR.KOUZA, FR.TESUU, FR.SOUKIN, FR.BANK_CD, FR.SITEN_ID, SH.SIHARAIDD, SH.SKIJITUDD, SH.V_YAKUJO FROM SS_TORI TR JOIN (SELECT TRCD, MIN(HJCD) AS HJCDMIN FROM SS_TORI GROUP BY TRCD) TRH ON TR.TRCD = TRH.TRCD AND TR.HJCD = TRH.HJCDMIN JOIN SS_TSHOH TS ON TS.TRCD = TR.TRCD AND TS.HJCD = TR.HJCD AND TS.SHO_ID = 1 JOIN SS_SHOHO SH ON SH.SHINO = TS.SHINO JOIN SS_SKUBN SK ON SK.SKBNCOD = SH.SKBNCOD JOIN SS_FRIGIN FR ON FR.TRCD = TR.TRCD AND FR.HJCD = TR.HJCD AND FR.GIN_ID = 1 WHERE LEN(TR.TRCD) < 13)
op_master_name: 取引先マスター（依頼先）

(SELECT DISTINCT
    kesn,
    ki,
    CAST(CAST(symd as CHAR(8)) AS DATE) as symd,
    CAST(CAST(eymd as CHAR(8)) AS DATE) as eymd
FROM
    (SELECT
        ki.KESN,
        v.*
    FROM aexp.a_ki ki
    JOIN aexp.a_volum2 v ON
        ki.ki = v.ki
    WHERE
        RIGHT(v.symd, 2) <> '00' AND
        RIGHT(v.eymd, 2) <> '00'
    ) t
)

(SELECT
    kmk.kesn,
    RTRIM(kmk.kicd) AS kicd,
    RTRIM(kmk.kcod) AS kcod,
    kmk.knmx,
    kmk.katt
FROM aexp.a_ki AS ki
JOIN kname AS kmk ON 
    kmk.kesn = ki.kesn
WHERE
    ki.ki in (0, 1, 2, 3)
)

(SELECT 
    bmn.kesn,
    RTRIM(bmn.bcod) AS bcod,
    bmn.bnam
FROM aexp.a_ki AS ki
JOIN bname AS bmn ON 
    bmn.kesn = ki.kesn
WHERE
    ki.ki in (0, 1, 2, 3)
)

(SELECT
    sbmn.kesn,
    sbmn.sbcd,
    sbname.bnam AS sbnam,
    zbmn.bcod,
    zbmn.bnam
FROM aexp.a_ki ki
JOIN sbtbl AS sbmn ON
    ki.kesn = sbmn.kesn
JOIN bname AS sbname ON
    sbmn.kesn = sbname.kesn AND
    sbmn.sbcd = sbname.bcod AND
    sbname.bflg = 1
JOIN bname AS zbmn ON
    sbmn.kesn = zbmn.kesn AND
    sbmn.bcod = zbmn.bcod AND
    zbmn.bflg = 0
WHERE
    ki.ki in (0, 1, 2, 3)
)

(SELECT
    kmk.kesn,
    kmk.sptn,
    kmk.szkm
FROM aexp.a_ki ki
JOIN sczkm kmk ON
    kmk.kesn = ki.kesn
WHERE
    kmk.skbn = 0 AND
    ki.ki in (0, 1, 2, 3)
)

(SELECT
    bmn.kesn,
    bmn.sptn,
    bmn.szbm
FROM aexp.a_ki AS ki
JOIN sczbm AS bmn ON
    bmn.kesn = ki.kesn
WHERE
    bmn.skbn = 0 and
    ki.ki in (0, 1, 2, 3)
)
